<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Zygo lowered to a buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Zygo lowered to a buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Alex. Brown said it lowered its recommendation on Zygo Corp to buy from strong buy.</p>
<p>-- Analyst was not immediately available to comment.</p>
<p>-- Shares tumbled 3-1/2 to 31-1/4 in early Nasdaq trade.</p>
